Use the standard library
This is how to is_palindrome of text:
  When text's length is 0, then:
    The answer is 1
  End when
  Remember that left is 0
  Remember that right is diff of text's length and 1
  Do this text's length times:
    When item left in text is not item right in text, then:
      The answer is 0
    End when
    Increase left
    Decrease right
    When left is at most right, then:
      Leave the loop
    End when
  End do
  The answer is 1
